nchor "></span><h2 class=3D"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default"=
>How can I afford to travel full time?</h2>				</div>
				</div>
				<div class=3D"elementor-element elementor-element-5fd3c8a elementor-wid=
get elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id=3D"5fd3c8a" data-element_type=3D"=
widget" data-widget_type=3D"text-editor.default">
				<div class=3D"elementor-widget-container">
									<p id=3D"viewer-3qluk">Before I jump into how to budget for full t=
ime travel, I wanted to answer this as it=E2=80=99s a question I get asked =
a lot =E2=80=93 <em>=E2=80=98how can you afford to travel full time?!=E2=80=
=99 </em>Some people we=E2=80=99ve met have even jokingly asked if we=E2=80=
=99re rich! (Ha! I wish!)</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p id=3D"viewer-1dd4t">At the time of writing this post, I=E2=80=99ve been =
travelling full time with my husband for just over a year. We set off in Se=
ptember 2021, spending 3 months in Europe, driving through the beautiful la=
ndscapes of <strong><a href=3D"https://www.curiousgoosetravel.com/post/thin=
gs-to-do-in-the-black-forest-germany" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer n=
oopener">Germany=E2=80=99s Black Forest</a>,</strong> visiting the <strong>=
<a href=3D"https://www.curiousgoosetravel.com/post/top-tips-for-visiting-ze=
rmatt-switzerland" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">Matterhorn=
 in Switzerland</a></strong> and enjoying life on the <strong><a href=3D"ht=
tps://www.curiousgoosetravel.com/post/great-places-to-visit-on-the-french-r=
iviera" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">French Riviera</a></s=
trong>. After a short stop back at home in the UK to spend Christmas with o=
ur families, we flew to <a href=3D"https://www.curiousgoosetravel.com/thail=
and" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener"><strong>Thailand</strong=
></a> in January 2022 and ended up loving it so much, we stayed there for 3=
 months. Following that, we visited Cambodia, spent <strong><a href=3D"http=
s://www.curiousgoosetravel.com/post/one-month-vietnam-itinerary" target=3D"=
_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">a month in Vietnam</a>,</strong> had <s=
trong><a href=3D"https://www.curiousgoosetravel.com/post/great-things-to-do=
-in-singapore" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">5 days in Sing=
apore</a>,</strong> then continued onto Malaysia and Bali before arriving i=
n Australia, where we are currently travelling around in a van for 3 months=
. After Australia we fly to New Zealand, where we=E2=80=99ll be enjoying va=
n life again for another 2 months.</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p id=3D"viewer-6jd4l">Neither of us work whilst we are travelling (althoug=
h we could both work remotely online if we chose to), so, you=E2=80=99re pr=
obably wondering how we afford to travel full time?</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p id=3D"viewer-fm95g">Well, the reality is that we spent quite a few years=
 saving really hard for our travels. We consciously decided that we didn=E2=
=80=99t want to have to work whilst we were taking this time out to travel,=
 so we knew we needed a plan and that involved a lot of saving! We made a r=
ough itinerary of where we wanted to travel and how long we wanted to spend=
 in each place. After that, we then set ourselves a travel budget and start=
ed saving! There really is no magic trick I=E2=80=99m afraid, but if you re=
ally want something and you are determined to work hard and focus on the en=
d goal, then you can make it happen.</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p id=3D"viewer-alhua"><strong><em>Check out my super simple, but effective=
 tips for </em></strong><a href=3D"https://www.curiousgoosetravel.com/post/=
12-tips-to-save-for-full-time-travel" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer n=
oopener"><strong><em>how to save for full time travel.</em></strong></a></p=
>								</div>
