				<div class=3D"elementor-element elementor-element-06c1d63 elementor-wid=
get elementor-widget-text-editor" data-id=3D"06c1d63" data-element_type=3D"=
widget" data-widget_type=3D"text-editor.default">
				<div class=3D"elementor-widget-container">
									<p id=3D"viewer-42kpd">It=E2=80=99s easy to get carried away dream=
ing of lying on the sandy <strong><a href=3D"https://www.curiousgoosetravel=
.com/post/11-beautiful-beaches-to-visit-in-phuket-thailand" target=3D"_blan=
k" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">beaches of Phuket</a>,</strong> in Thailand =
or <strong><a href=3D"https://www.curiousgoosetravel.com/post/visiting-udaw=
alawe-national-park" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer noopener">visiting=
 elephants in Sri Lanka</a></strong>, but before that becomes a reality, yo=
u need to plan your travel budget.</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p id=3D"viewer-7jkvv">Without knowing how much things cost and how much mo=
ney you will actually need to travel, you=E2=80=99ll run out of money very =
quickly. No-one wants to have to cut their trip short because they don=E2=
=80=99t have any money left!</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p id=3D"viewer-d10d2">How much money you will need to travel full time wil=
l be different for everyone as it is dependant on a number of things:</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:list --></p>
<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Destination (the place or places you want to travel to)</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Duration (how long you hope to spend in each place)</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>Your style of travel (the standard of accommodation, transport, food an=
d drink you are happy with)</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item -->
<li>What activities you plan to do (if you have any bucket list activities =
you want to tick off such as a helicopter ride over the Grand Canyon or <st=
rong><a href=3D"https://bit.ly/thundercatCG" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noref=
errer noopener">snorkel in the Whitsundays</a>,</strong> these things will =
evidently cost more).</li>
<!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>
<p><!-- /wp:list --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p id=3D"viewer-2qhvb">The next 9 steps will guide you through how to creat=
e your travel budget. This includes not only setting your budget for <em>wh=
ilst</em> you are travelling, but also your pre-departure budget, emergency=
 travel funds budget, an ongoing expenses budget and a post travel budget.<=
/p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p id=3D"viewer-9l6qr">That may sound overwhelming, but I promise you it is=
 really quite simple once you get started and hopefully this guide will hel=
p you break it down into more manageable chunks.</p>
<p><!-- /wp:paragraph --><!-- wp:paragraph --></p>
<p id=3D"viewer-fphls">And to make it even easier for you, I=E2=80=99ve sha=
red my own Travel Budget Spreadsheet as a temple which you can download and=
 use for yourself. It is editable so you can make any changes you might wan=
t too.</p>								</div>
