ccommodation, transport and the price of meals and drinks. Read blogs, watc=
h YouTube videos but also do some research yourself on sites such as bookin=
g.com to see how much accommodation is on average, or on sites like <strong=
><a href=3D"https://bit.ly/viatorCG" target=3D"_blank" rel=3D"noreferrer no=
opener">Viator</a> </strong>to see how much tours and activities might be.<=
/p>
